des: "Just a simple, smoky sweet rub I created one day. If you're looking for more bite then add a bit more cayenne pepper. Works great for oven-to-grill ribs! Apply to your ribs of choice and enjoy!"
ins: Whisk paprika, light brown sugar, dark brown sugar, white sugar, sea salt, ground black pepper, garlic powder, iodized salt, onion powder, cumin, and cayenne pepper together in a bowl until smooth.
